## 3. Validation UX

### 3.1 Timing

- **onBlur**: Validate individual field when user leaves it
- **onChange**: Clear existing error as user types (don't show new errors while typing)
- **onSubmit**: Validate all fields, show error summary, focus first errored field

### 3.2 Error Display

- Inline error below field: `<p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-1 ml-1">`
- Error summary panel at top of form on submit (clickable rows that focus the errored field)
- Error summary uses `role="alert"` so screen readers announce it
- Error panel header shows count: "Please fix 3 errors below"

### 3.3 Field States (Visual)

| State | Border | Background | Label Color |
|-------|--------|------------|-------------|
| Default | `border-slate-200` | `bg-white` | `text-slate-400` |
| Focused | `border-orange-400 outline-orange-100` | `bg-white` | `text-orange-500` |
| Filled (valid) | `border-emerald-400 outline-emerald-100` | `bg-emerald-50/40` | `text-emerald-600` |
| Error | `border-red-300 outline-red-100` | `bg-red-50/40` | `text-red-500` |

### 3.4 Status Icons (Right Side of Input)

| State | Icon |
|-------|------|
| Error | `<XCircle>` red |
| Valid | `<CheckCircle2>` green |
| Checking | `<Loader2>` orange, spinning |

### 3.5 Email Validation Regex

```js
/^[a-zA-Z0-9._%+-]+@[a-zA-Z0-9]([a-zA-Z0-9-]*[a-zA-Z0-9])?(\.[a-zA-Z0-9]([a-zA-Z0-9-]*[a-zA-Z0-9])?)*\.[a-zA-Z]{2,12}$/
```

### 3.6 Password Rules

All four must pass to submit:
1. Length >= 8 characters
2. At least one uppercase letter (A-Z)
3. At least one number (0-9)
4. At least one special character (!@#$...)

